Title: A Glowing Memento
Description:
<An unusually persistent ember draws your eye. It glows with a pure, primal heat.> 

<Vyranoth would be interested in this.>
ObjectivesText: Bring the Everglowing Ember to Vyranoth in Amirdrassil or the Central Encampment in the Emerald Dream.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak to Vyranoth in Amirdrassil or the Central Encampment in the Emerald Dream.
